languages.text: Выстрел поразил цель. Неизвестный корабль еще мгновение продолжал движение... а затем его изображение на приборах превратилось в сноп искр. Конечно же, один выстрел не мог полностью уничтожить столь большое судно... Однако столкновения с обломками так и не произошло.

The shell hit its target. The unidentified ship held its course for a moment longer... and then it vanished, leaving only flashes of light in its wake. A single projectile is not enough to destroy a ship of that size... What's more, our ship collided with no debris.

traits.locale_text: The missile hit the target. The unidentified ship stayed on its course for while, and then disappeared from our radars, leaving only flashes of light and white noise. One missile is not enough to destroy a ship such size... What's more, there was no debris left.

languages.text: 炮弹击中了目标。那艘身份不明的舰船沿着原本的方向继续行驶了一段时间……之后就凭空消失了，只留下了一阵闪光。一枚炮弹根本不足以摧毁这么大的飞船……不仅如此，我们的飞船也没有撞上任何飞船残片。

languages.text: El proyectil alcanza su objetivo. La nave no identificada mantiene el rumbo durante un instante... y desaparece, dejando solo destellos de luz. Un solo proyectil no destruiría una nave de ese tamaño... y además nuestra nave no ha colisionado con sus restos.
languages.original_text: The shell hit its target. The unidentified ship held its course for a moment longer... and then it vanished, leaving only flashes of light in its wake. A single projectile is not enough to destroy a ship of that size... What's more, our ship collided with no debris.

languages.text: 弾は目標に命中した。正体不明の船は、しばらく航路を維持し…閃光を残して消えていった。あの大きさの船を破壊するには、弾丸一発では不十分のはずだが…。しかも、こちらの船には衝突した痕ひとつなかった。

languages.text: Das Geschoss hat sein Ziel getroffen. Das unbekannte Schiff hielt seinen Kurs noch ein wenig länger ... und verschwand dann. Zurück blieben nur Lichtblitze. Ein einziges Projektil reicht nicht aus, um ein Schiff von dieser Größe zu zerstören ... Und: Unser Schiff kollidierte mit keinem Wrackteilen.
languages.original_text: The shell hit its target. The unidentified ship held its course for a moment longer... and then it vanished, leaving only flashes of light in its wake. A single projectile is not enough to destroy a ship of that size... What's more, our ship collided with no debris.

languages.text: L'obus a atteint sa cible. Le vaisseau non identifié maintient son cap pendant un moment... avant de disparaître en ne laissant que des rais de lumière dans son sillage. Un seul projectile ne suffit pas à détruire un vaisseau de cette taille. De plus, notre vaisseau n'a percuté aucun débris.

languages.text: Mermi, hedefe isabet etti. Tanımlanamayan gemi bir an daha rotasını korudu, ardından yalnızca ışık patlamaları bırakarak ortadan kayboldu. Bu boyutta bir gemiyi tek bir mermiyle yok etmek mümkün değil. Dahası, gemimiz hiçbir enkaz parçasıyla çarpışmadı.
